Issue:Client raising complaint that proper route was not followed for a specific transaction < trxn no >
Outcome: If 1 rows returned from SQL execution then Correct Route was followed ,  then inform with Response "Route Name is correct".
If no rows retuned from SQL execution then incorrect Route was followed ,  then inform with Response "Route Name is Incorrect".

Analysis:
If 1 rows returned from SQL execution then Correct Route was followed ,  then inform with Response "Route Name is correct".
If no rows retuned from SQL execution then incorrect Route was followed ,  then inform with Response "Route Name is Incorrect".
